                            <comment id="17501254" author="JIRAUSER282521" created="Fri, 4 Mar 2022 10:41:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I hit a failure in HtmlLayoutTest (Mac and CentOS).&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;ERROR&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; &#160; HtmlLayoutTest.testLayoutWithDatePatternFixedFormat:242-&amp;gt;testLayoutWithDatePatternFixedFormat:273 Incorrect date=&amp;lt;td&amp;gt;2012-11-02T14:34:02,123+05&amp;lt;/td&amp;gt;, format=ISO8601_OFFSET_DATE_TIME_HH, timezone=null ==&amp;gt; expected: &amp;lt;&amp;lt;td&amp;gt;2012-11-02T14:34:02,123+0530&amp;lt;/td&amp;gt;&amp;gt; but was: &amp;lt;&amp;lt;td&amp;gt;2012-11-02T14:34:02,123+05&amp;lt;/td&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;


